:"He studies the numbers, studies the law"},{"s":77,"e":79.22,"text":"Turns every hard day into awe"},{"s":79.52,"e":81.74,"text":"Blind, not broken, he moves with soul"},{"s":81.86,"e":84.3,"text":"Turned a soup-line mile into a city goal"},{"s":84.3,"e":87.04,"text":"From the rail to the ballot, from the block to the booth"},{"s":87.04,"e":89.58,"text":"He don’t just speak hope, he delivers the truth"},{"s":89.94,"e":92.1,"text":"Hear that laugh, hear that pace"},{"s":92.12,"e":94.74,"text":"Every setback trying, but he won’t chase"},{"s":94.96,"e":97.24,"text":"He’s got hunger in his chest"},{"s":97.24,"e":99.98,"text":"And a map nobody else can guess"},{"s":100.18,"e":104.04,"text":"One stop higher, one stop higher"},{"s":104.74,"e":109.08,"text":"Mikewell keep going, straight through the fire"},{"s":110.2,"e":114.34,"text":"One stop higher, one stop higher"},{"s":114.6,"e":119.42,"text":"From the station floor to the mayor’s wire"},{"s":120.08,"e":121.98,"text":"(one stop higher)"},{"s":122.78,"e":124.36,"text":"(one stop higher)"},{"s":124.86,"e":127.02,"text":"They said wait your turn"},{"s":127.56,"e":129.62,"text":"He said watch me learn"},{"s":130.2,"e":132.26,"text":"They said take the low road"},{"s":132.4,"e":134.92,"text":"He said I’m built for the climb"},{"s":135.34,"e":137.78,"text":"Now the whole town knows"},{"s":137.78,"e":140.14,"text":"How the young king grows"},{"s":140.14,"e":143,"text":"One train ride, one bold dream"},{"s":143.26,"e":146.14,"text":"One name up on the front line"},{"s":149.5,"e":153.08,"text":"One stop higher, one stop higher"},{"s":153.74,"e":158.06,"text":"Mikewell keep going, straight through the fire"},{"s":159.32,"e":163.32,"text":"One stop higher, one stop higher"},{"s":163.4,"e":168.3,"text":"From the station floor to the mayor’s wire"},{"s":169.3,"e":173.56,"text":"One stop higher, one stop higher"},{"s":173.7,"e":178.56,"text":"Scholarship shine, let the whole city admire"},{"s":179.3,"e":181.14,"text":"(one stop higher)"},{"s":184.32,"e":186.3,"text":"(one stop higher)"}],"duration":191.96,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.235Z","stats":{"whisperWords":376,"polishedWords":342,"matched":326,"matchRate":0.953}}